Seminar on Kim Jong Il's Work Held in Mexico
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Pyongyang, May 25 (KCNA) -- A seminar on General Secretary Kim Jong Il's famous work "Giving Priority to Ideological Work Is Essential For Accomplishing Socialism" was held by the Mexican Committee for the Study of Kimilsungism on May 19 on the occasion of the 44th anniversary of the start of his work at the Central Committee of the Workers' Party of Korea. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
 Ramon Jimenez Lopez, President of the Mexican committee, referred to the significance of the seminar and introduced the main contents of the work. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;
